# dh_install file list for syauth v0.1.0.
#
# Most file paths are written directly by override_dh_auto_install in
# debian/rules so they land with explicit modes (the .so and the
# binary). This file lists the additional doc + license files that
# debhelper installs with default permissions.
README.md usr/share/doc/syauth/
docs/security.md usr/share/doc/syauth/
docs/android-setup.md usr/share/doc/syauth/
LICENSE usr/share/doc/syauth/
